c_ops_ground = []
sts = f_ground_states_uncoupled()
for sigma_k in jmat(1/2):
    c = tensor(identity(4), sigma_k).transform(sts[1])
    c.dims = [[8], [8]]
    tmp = np.zeros(shape=(16,16), dtype=np.cdouble)
    tmp[:8,:8] = c
    c_ops_ground.append((2e3)**(1/2)*Qobj(tmp))
